snippet.title: Sushi Ben VR - Official Gameplay Video | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description: Get another look at Sushi Ben, an upcoming VR narrative adventure game where you must save a local sushi restaurant from going out of business. Sushi Ben is coming to major VR headsets in 2023.
